==Beschreibung==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The [[Image:BIM_Shape2DCut.svg|24px]] [[BIM_Shape2DCut|BIM Shape2DCut]] tool inherits from [[Image:BIM_Shape2DView.svg|24px]] [[BIM_Shape2DView|BIM Shape2DView]]. It performs the same initial action but then sets the resulting object's {{PropertyData|Projection Mode}} to {{Value|Cutfaces}}. This means the final 2D object will only display the geometry that is directly intersected by the section plane, creating a true "section cut" view.
</div>

